==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kymograph
<hw>Ky"mo*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ wave +
<ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>An instrument for
measuring, and recording graphically, the pressure of the blood in any
of the blood vessels of a living animal; -- called also
<altname>kymographion</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kymographic</ent>⟦br⟧
